Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:07.65,CN,Shizuka,0,0,0,,反正也吃不完
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:10.53,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:14.79,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,給我麵包的靜香
